<BaseLayout title="About Korea Tax Guide for Foreigners" description="Learn what Korea Tax Guide for Foreigners does, who it helps, and why it is not an official government or personal tax advice website.">
  <main class="section narrow article">
    <h1>About Korea Tax Guide for Foreigners</h1>
    <p>This website helps foreigners in Korea understand common tax filing procedures, Hometax steps, refund checks, and tax documents. We explain complicated Korean tax terms in simple English and connect each topic to practical step-by-step guides.</p>
    <p>This website is not an official government website. It does not provide personal tax advice, tax agency services, legal advice, immigration advice, or refund guarantees.</p>
    <p>Users should check official sources or consult a qualified professional for their own situation, especially when residency, overseas income, business income, treaty rules, or visa documents are involved.</p>
  </main>
